Package it.unipr.sowide.actodes.service.logging.content

Class Execution

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.unipr.sowide.actodes.service.logging.content.Log
      • it.unipr.sowide.actodes.service.logging.content.Execution
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public final class Execution
extends Log
    The Execution class is used for informing about the execution time and the number of actors created during the execution of the actor space. For applications involving passive actors it provides the number of scheduling cycles too.
